This paper focuses on multimodal biometric identification using face images, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms such as MLP, LVQ, and RBF for classification purposes, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges of face recognition systems, which can be related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
